files.name: .gitignore
files.content:
node_modules
dist
.nyc_output
coverage
.next
examples/react/db.json
examples/react/last-browser-open
*.tsbuildinfo
.docusaurus
build
.env

files.name: .npmrc
files.content:
workspace-concurrency=4
public-hoist-pattern[]=@types/*
public-hoist-pattern[]=esbuild
public-hoist-pattern[]=typescript
public-hoist-pattern[]=prettier
public-hoist-pattern[]=ts-jest
public-hoist-pattern[]=jest
public-hoist-pattern[]=rollup*
public-hoist-pattern[]=@rollup*
prefer-workspace-packages=true

files.name: README.md
files.content:
a GraphQL client built for rapid iteration.

--- Head over to [gqless.com](https://gqless.com), to explore features and documentation. --- ## Get involved Documentation, bug reports, pull requests, and all other contributions are welcome! See [`CONTRIBUTING.md`](CONTRIBUTING.md). ## [Sponsors](https://opencollective.com/gqless/contribute) Docs powered by [Vercel](https://vercel.com/?utm_source=gqless&utm_campaign=oss)

files.name: dev-react.mjs
dev.mjs
package.json
files.content:
{
  "name": "gqless_monorepo",
  "private": true,
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/gqless/gqless.git"
  },
  "license": "MIT",
  "type": "module",
  "scripts": {
    "build": "pnpm build -r --stream",
    "build:docs": "pnpm build:website",
    "build:website": "pnpm -r --filter website docs:build",
    "changeset": "changeset",
    "ci:release": "pnpm -r publish --access public --no-git-checks",
    "ci:version": "changeset version && pnpm i --no-frozen-lockfile --lockfile-only --ignore-scripts",
    "clean": "rimraf packages/*/dist packages/*/coverage packages/*/.nyc_output packages/*/*.tsbuildinfo",
    "dev": "pnpm clean && node dev.mjs",
    "dev:mercurius": "pnpm -r exec --filter gqless -- tsc -m commonjs && concurrently \"pnpm -r --filter mercurius-example test:watch\" \"pnpm -r --filter gqless start\"",
    "dev:nodemon": "pnpm prepare -r --no-bail && pnpm test -r --no-bail --no-sort --stream",
    "dev:react": "node dev-react.mjs",
    "dev:start": "pnpm start -r --no-bail --no-sort",
    "dev:test": "pnpm test:watch -r --no-bail --no-sort --stream",
    "docs:build": "pnpm build:website && pretty-quick",
    "prepare": "husky install",
    "pretty": "pretty-quick",
    "publish:all": "changeset version && pnpm i && pnpm test && pnpm -r publish --access public",
    "test": "jest --clearCache && pnpm test -r --no-sort --no-bail --stream",
    "website": "pnpm -r --filter website start",
    "website:build": "pnpm -r --filter website docs:build && pretty-quick"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "bufferutil": "^4.0.3",
    "build-utils": "workspace:^1.0.0",
    "esbuild": "^0.11.12",
    "jest": "^26.6.3",
    "nodemon": "^2.0.7",
    "open": "^8.0.6",
    "ts-jest": "^26.5.5",
    "ts-node": "^9.1.1",
    "tslib": "^2.2.0",
    "tsup": "^4.9.1",
    "typescript": "^4.2.4",
    "utf-8-validate": "^5.0.4",
    "wait-on": "^5.3.0"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@babel/plugin-proposal-nullish-coalescing-operator": "^7.13.8",
    "@babel/plugin-proposal-optional-chaining": "^7.13.12",
    "@changesets/cli": "^2.16.0",
    "@types/node": "^14.14.41",
    "concurrently": "^6.0.2",
    "fkill": "^7.1.1",
    "husky": "^6.0.0",
    "prettier": "^2.2.1",
    "pretty-quick": "^3.1.0",
    "rimraf": "^3.0.2"
  },
  "engines": {
    "pnpm": ">=6.0.2"
  },
  "pnpm": {
    "overrides": {
      "typescript": "^4.2.4",
      "jest": "^26.6.3",
      "ts-jest": "^26.5.5",
      "prettier": "^2.2.1",
      "esbuild": "^0.11.12",
      "@types/node": "^14.14.41"
    }
  }
}
